{"tid":614152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DLLM唔係親眼見我都唔信","createTime":"2018-04-02T09:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-05T07:52:23.000Z","uid":29090,"like":148,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"038d158fe7a4961c3027327f9876db3685a7b64a","tid":614152,"uid":29090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:20:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/170929_5325d021c2d26ba5818a93f6f1aa9bbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F170929_5325d021c2d26ba5818a93f6f1aa9bbd.jpg&h=fba448ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/171114_777d84e24e3521357ed49a42f282fb05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F171114_777d84e24e3521357ed49a42f282fb05.jpg&h=d5714bf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/02/171845_a72bf1fbb4ff6fa800aa4c686caf5a0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F02%2F171845_a72bf1fbb4ff6fa800aa4c686caf5a0f.jpg&h=3f93853a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，頭先去食個M記<br />\n點知一聽見隔離枱陰啲陰啲咁講支那語<br />\n（因為平時講支那語嘅人點會咁細聲）<br />\n就睇下佢咩人<br />\n<br />\n一睇原來係DSE雞<br />\n鬼鬼鼠鼠傾計又好似唔識講廣東話<br />\n就諗起之前一篇新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180322/2_577838_0/-%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E4%BA%BA%E7%8E%A9%E5%9F%8BDSE-%E8%B8%A2%E7%88%86-%E8%BF%91%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E9%AB%98%E8%80%83%E7%94%9F%E5%90%BC%E4%BD%8FDSE-%E6%B8%AF%E8%A3%9C%E7%BF%92%E7%A4%BE%E9%96%8B%E7%8F%AD%E5%8C%85%E5%85%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180322%2F2_577838_0%2F-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%258E%25A9%25E5%259F%258BDSE-%25E8%25B8%25A2%25E7%2588%2586-%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%258D%2583%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598%25E8%2580%2583%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2590%25BC%25E4%25BD%258FDSE-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25A3%259C%25E7%25BF%2592%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%258F%25AD%25E5%258C%2585%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8&d=oJJwycnxtbbIxqRg37QJgTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=8d0e1f92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180322%2F2_577838_0%2F-%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2599%25B8%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%258E%25A9%25E5%259F%258BDSE-%25E8%25B8%25A2%25E7%2588%2586-%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%258D%2583%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%25AB%2598%25E8%2580%2583%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2590%25BC%25E4%25BD%258FDSE-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25A3%259C%25E7%25BF%2592%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%258F%25AD%25E5%258C%2585%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8&h=c8a0fcc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180322/2_577838_0/-%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%B8%E4%BA%BA%E7%8E%A9%E5%9F%8BDSE-%E8%B8%A2%E7%88%86-%E8%BF%91%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E9%AB%98%E8%80%83%E7%94%9F%E5%90%BC%E4%BD%8FDSE-%E6%B8%AF%E8%A3%9C%E7%BF%92%E7%A4%BE%E9%96%8B%E7%8F%AD%E5%8C%85%E5%85%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8</a><br />\n<br />\n之前睇到篇咁嘅新聞我仲半信半疑<br />\n你d 支那學霸有500分 就non jupas 身份入3大啦<br />\n<br />\n但諗深一層依家有300分就可以入三大<br />\n就梗係輕輕鬆鬆睇個墳場必備，打下PUBG先啦<br />\n瞓喺度都贏你，等你班00後繼續屌鳩自己人，考試寫殘體字啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:你可以當我看圖作故事，我出呢篇野就係睇唔過眼d 支那人咁得戚"},{"pid":"12a4f0a56147f1a2864927dd628eedbe1b23f818","tid":614152,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37c9bce018fdb20c0a2fab33e6c8213965400afc","tid":614152,"uid":107364,"like":25,"dislike":25,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-02T09:27:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪